b'Policy Coverage'
b'Prohibition of Sex Discrimination, Sexual Harassment and Sexual Misconduct Policy'
b'Prohibition of Sex Discrimination, Sexual Harassment and Sexual Misconduct Policy'
b'This policy applies to sexual misconduct that is alleged to have been committed by a UIC student, student organization, faculty or staff member:\na) On campus, which includes the University of Illinois Hospital and Health Sciences System\nb) Off campus, in connection with a University recognized program or activity\nc) Off campus, in a manner that may pose an obvious and serious threat of harm or may have the effect of creating a hostile educational environment for any member of the University community.'
b'Sexual misconduct committed by student-employees in the context of their employment will be addressed in accordance with the University\xe2\x80\x99s employment policies and the Student Disciplinary policy.'
b'Note: Individuals at a regional site of the UIC campus should also refer to their local site publications and websites for additional policies, reporting information pertaining to their sites, and information on available resources on and off site.'
